strings:
<voice_0x01000D5E><se_low>Yangus: So this is it, eh...?
The Venus' tear!
You beauty!

<voice_0x01000D5F><se_low>Yangus: You know, guv...
Last time I tried to get this stone,
I done it for Red.
<voice_0x01000D60><se_low>Yangus: Now we're just rivals, I guess, but I actually used to 'ave a bit of a thing for Red.
<voice_0x01000D61><se_low>Yangus: Back in them days she weren't a scary old bird like she is now. An' I was well green.

<voice_0x01000D62><se_low>Yangus: So I thought I'd get her the Venus' tear to
impress her, like. But I ended up doin' meself
an injury an' I 'ad to leave it.
<voice_0x01000D63><se_low>Yangus: Never thought I'd end up gettin' it like this, though!
<voice_0x01000D64><se_low>Yangus: I wonder 'ow it would've all turned out if I 'ad got it back then, eh?
<voice_0x01000D65><se_low>Yangus: Anyway, just me old wounds. Would ya mind keepin' this to yerself, guv? Ain't the kind o' thing ya want goin' around.
